        1/day each: <emphasis>calm emotions</emphasis>, <emphasis>dispel
        evil and good</emphasis>, <emphasis>entangle</emphasis>
      </para>
      <para>
        <emphasis role="strong"><emphasis>Magic
        Resistance</emphasis></emphasis>. The unicorn has advantage on
        saving throws against spells and other magical effects.
      </para>
      <para>
        <emphasis role="strong"><emphasis>Magic
        Weapons</emphasis></emphasis>. The unicorn’s weapon attacks are
        magical.
      </para>
      <section xml:id="actions-191">
