        <para>
          <emphasis role="strong"><emphasis>Multiattack</emphasis></emphasis>.
          The unicorn makes two attacks: one with its hooves and one
          with its horn.
        </para>
        <para>
          <emphasis role="strong"><emphasis>Hooves</emphasis></emphasis>.
